## 1. Executive Summary 💼

UNL Campus Pulse is a **full-stack, data-driven campus observability platform** designed to give students, administrators, and stakeholders a **single pane of glass** into:

- Real-time and simulated **building occupancy** 📈
- **Course scheduling density** and space utilization 📚
- **Dining and facility wait times** 🍔⏱️
- **Spatial analytics** over a 3D, Mapbox-powered representation of the UNL campus 🗺️🏢

Built with a **Next.js 16** frontend, a **Python-based data backend**, and a curated set of **map + deck.gl visualizations**, Campus Pulse enables:

- Smarter routing decisions
- Strategic space planning
- Higher student satisfaction
- Extremely compelling demo moments for any stakeholder presentation 😎

This README PRO MAX is the **definitive, long-form, enterprise-ready documentation artifact** that walks through **every piece** of this repo — and yes, it is intentionally over-the-top.

